OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChina to finally reopen    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fborders to foreign tourists
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, China is to resume issuing visas to    
OL,6, foreign tourists for the first time    
OL,7, since the Covid pandemic broke out     
OL,8, three years ago.                       
OL,10,FThe major easing of restrictions comes 
OL,11,Fafter Beijing declared victory over the
OL,12,Fvirus and retreats from a zero-Covid   
OL,13,Fstrategy that has hurt its economy.    
OL,15,FFrom 15 March, foreign offices can     
OL,16,Fprocess applications for Chinese visas.
OL,18,FVisa-free entry will also resume in    
OL,19,FHainan Island and Shanghai for cruise  
OL,20,Fships.                                 
